726817f-a.title: Queens: Grand Central Parkwa - 77th Street
726817f-a.text:
Grand Central Parkway, west from 77th Street and Astoria BBoulevard, showing the borough-wide thoroughfare under construction.
October 28, 1935
P. L. Sperr

726809f-b.title: Queens: Grand Central Parkwa - 77th Avenue
726809f-b.text:
Grand Central Parkway, south from near 77th Avenue, across the lIndependent System Subway yards. This area shows the extensive highway junctions of Grand Central Parkway, Union Turnpike and the Interboro Parkway.
Views 1,2: May 30, 1939
View 3: June 29, 1936
P. L. Sperr
